FBIS3-34899 "drnes032_l_94012" FBIS-NES-94-032 Document Type:Daily Report 16 Feb 1994 ISRAEL Arab Shot Dead by IDF During Dispersal of Riot TA1502085094 Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el in Hebrew 0800 GMT 15 Feb 94 TA1502085094 Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el Language: Hebrew Article Type:BFN [Text] A local youth was shot dead by the IDF [Israel Defense Forces] in Rafah's Shabura refugee camp when soldiers dispersed a riot which broke out near the home of Faris Abu-Zakar, who died of wounds sustained in a clash with soldiers. Abu-Zakar was a member of the Popular Front for the Liberation of Palestine.
